, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-436x300.jpg 436w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-400x275.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-800x550.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-696x478.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-1392x956.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-1068x734.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1476px) 100vw, 1476px" /></p><p>据报道，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spike-lee">斯派克·李</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/denzel-washington">丹泽尔·华盛顿</a>第五次合作，重新构思黑泽明 1963 年的犯罪剧<em>《High And Low》</em> 。</p><p>这对搭档之前的项目包括<em>《马尔科姆·X》</em> 、 <em>《He Got Game》</em>和<em>《局内人》</em> ，将于三月开始拍摄改编版。原版电影改编自艾德·麦克贝恩的小说<em>《国王的赎金》</em> ，三船敏郎饰演一名富翁，被迫为雇员被绑架的儿子支付赎金。</p><p> 2008年，有报道称<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/martin-scorsese">马丁·斯科塞斯</a>将翻拍这个故事，但该项目从未实施。</p><p>李此前曾表达过他对黑泽明的钦佩，声称他 1986 年的喜剧<em>《她一定要拥有它》</em>受到了这位日本导演 1950 年的戏剧<em>《罗生门》</em>的影响。</p><p>翻拍版<em>《High And Low》</em>将由 A24 在电影院上映，然后在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple-tv">Apple TV+</a>上上映（据<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/film/2024/feb/08/spike-lee-denzel-washington-akira-kurosawa-movie-remake" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a>报道）。 </p><figure id="attachment_3121456" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3121456" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3121456" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Spike-Lee-main-new.jpg" alt="斯派克·李" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Spike-Lee-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Spike-Lee-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Spike-Lee-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Spike-Lee-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Spike-Lee-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Spike-Lee-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3121456" class="wp-caption-text">导演斯派克·李 图片来源：Marc Piasecki/FilmMagic</figcaption></figure><p>前大学篮球运动员、模特、剧作家艾伦·福克斯将撰写剧本。福克斯目前还在制作<em>《石器时代女王》</em>的剧本，该片讲述了一名模特成为杂草贩子的故事。据报道，达科塔·约翰逊正在洽谈主演事宜。</p><p>华盛顿接下来将与保罗·梅斯卡尔一起出演雷德利·斯科特的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/paul-mescal-says-hes-finally-finished-filming-gladiator-3574224"><em>《角斗士 2》</em></a> 。这位演员最后一次与李合作是在 2006 年的惊悚片<em>《局内人》</em>中。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/denzel-washington-to-play-hannibal-in-biopic-by-gladiator-writer-3538614">华盛顿在<em>《角斗士》</em>作家约翰·洛根的传记片中饰演古代迦太基将军汉尼拔</a>。安提奥·福卡 (Antione Fuqua) 电影即将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>上映，讲述了对罗马共和国构成最大威胁的著名军事领袖的故事，他率领军队骑着大象越过阿尔卑斯山，从北方进攻罗​​马。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/denzel-washinton-hannibal-sparks-race-controversy-in-tunisia-3557814">华盛顿的选角消息在这位军事指挥官的祖国突尼斯引发了争议</a>，许多人抱怨这位历史人物被描绘成非洲黑人。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/spike-lee-and-denzel-washington-reunite-to-remake-akira-kurosawa-crime-drama-3585059">斯派克·李和丹泽尔·华盛顿再度联手翻拍黑泽明犯罪剧，</a>首映于<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a> 。</p> ;
