ER">(Liam</a> Gallagher) 一起参加雷丁音乐节<a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-festival-2022">(Reading &amp; Leeds)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blink-182">Blink-182 音乐节</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-announce-stacked-line-up-for-2024-3545261">Primavera Sound 音乐节</a>和环<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/zach-bryan-lana-del-rey-odesza-headline-hangout-festival-2024-3568922">聊音乐节 (Hangout Festival) 等音乐节</a>。</p><p>拉娜·德雷 (Lana Del Rey) 发帖称，在 2024 年格莱美颁奖典礼首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lana-del-rey-did-not-feel-one-ounce-of-negative-emotion-during-2024-grammys-3585037">时，她“没有感受到一丝负面情绪”</a> 。</p> ;
