circle">《印第安纳琼斯与大圆》</a> 、《<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/sea-of-thieves">盗贼之海</a>》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/halo">《光环》</a></em>和<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/gears-of-war">《战争机器》</a></em>可以在 PlayStation 5 上玩，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/hi-fi-rush"><em>《Hi-Fi Rush》</em></a>则可以在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>上玩。即将登陆<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/nintendo-switch">任天堂 Switch</a> 。</p><p>为了淡化这些谣言，Xbox 老板<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-boss-to-share-vision-for-the-future-next-week-following-backlash-over-rumours-3583793">Phil Spencer 本周在社交媒体上告诉粉丝，公司正在倾听他们的意见</a>。 “我们听到你的声音了，”他说。 “我们一直在计划下周举行一次业务更新活动，我们期待与您分享更多关于我们未来愿景的细节，”他继续说道，然后要求粉丝“继续关注”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3441123" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3441123" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3441123" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Xbox-wireless-controller-Credit-Microsoft-Xbox@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Xbox 无线控制器" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Xbox-wireless-controller-Credit-Microsoft-Xbox@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Xbox-wireless-controller-Credit-Microsoft-Xbox@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Xbox-wireless-controller-Credit-Microsoft-Xbox@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Xbox-wireless-controller-Credit-Microsoft-Xbox@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Xbox-wireless-controller-Credit-Microsoft-Xbox@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Xbox-wireless-controller-Credit-Microsoft-Xbox@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3441123" class="wp-caption-text"> Xbox 无线控制器。图片来源：微软 Xbox</figcaption></figure><p>斯宾塞此前曾公开谈论过 Xbox、PlayStation 和任天堂用户之间的所谓竞争。 2020 年，他称主机大战<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-boss-says-console-wars-is-one-of-the-worst-things-about-the-industry-2824319">是“该行业最糟糕的事情之一”。</a></p><p> “我对不断增长的游戏市场更感兴趣，而不是我自己分得别人的份额，”他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-boss-phil-spencer-has-zero-energy-for-console-wars-3113074">在第二年补充道</a>。 “这就是为什么我们专注于交叉游戏和交叉保存等事情。我思考了这些场景，解释了为什么你和我可能无法一起玩游戏，这不应该是因为你购买的游戏机与我购买的游戏机不同。”</p><p>然而，上个月斯宾塞证实该公司“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-has-no-plans-to-bring-game-pass-to-nintendo-or-playstation-3552848">没有计划</a>”将 Game Pass 引入任天堂或 PlayStation，此前首席财务官 Tim Stuart 表示计划将该服务引入“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/gaming-news/xbox-game-pass-might-be-coming-to-playstation-and-nintendo-switch-3552364">每个可以玩游戏的屏幕</a>”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/fable-avowed-and-hellblade-2-pages-remove-xbox-game-pass-mentions-3585026">“寓言”、“宣誓”和“地狱之刃 2”页面删除 Xbox Game Pass 提及的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
凯撒酋长队的瑞奇·威尔逊回应马克·E·史密斯和绿洲的侮辱https://www.nme.com/news/music/kaiser-chiefs-ricky-wilson-responds-to-insults-received-from-mark-e-smith-and-oasis-3584979?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=凯撒酋长瑞奇威尔逊回应来自马克史密斯和绿洲的侮辱Tom SkinnerFri, 09 Feb 2024 11:31:14 +0000 Music NewsNewsBritpopIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3584979 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/RickyWilson-Liam-Gallagher-Mark-E-Smith.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马克·E·史密斯（左）、瑞奇·威尔逊（中）和利亚姆·加拉格尔（右）的三张并排照片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/RickyWilson-Liam-Gallagher-Mark-E-Smith.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/RickyWilson-Liam-Gallagher-Mark-E-Smith-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/RickyWilson-Liam-Gallagher-Mark-E-Smith-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/RickyWilson-Liam-Gallagher-Mark-E-Smith-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/RickyWilson-Liam-Gallagher-Mark-E-Smith-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/RickyWilson-Liam-Gallagher-Mark-E-Smith-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “[我]不是那种会因为利亚姆·加拉格尔所说的关于我的事情而与他对质的人”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kaiser-chiefs-ricky-wilson-responds-to-insults-received-from-mark-e-smith-and-oasis-3584979">凯撒酋长队的瑞奇·威尔逊 (Ricky Wilson) 对马克·E·史密斯 (Mark E. Smith) 和绿洲 (Oasis) 的侮辱做出回应，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/RickyWilson-Liam-Gallagher-Mark-E-Smith.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马克·E·史密斯（左）、瑞奇·威尔逊（中）和利亚姆·加拉格尔（右）的三张并排照片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/RickyWilson-Liam-Gallagher-Mark-E-Smith.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/RickyWilson-Liam-Gallagher-Mark-E-Smith-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/RickyWilson-Liam-Gallagher-Mark-E-Smith-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/RickyWilson-Liam-Gallagher-Mark-E-Smith-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/RickyWilson-Liam-Gallagher-Mark-E-Smith-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/RickyWilson-Liam-Gallagher-Mark-E-Smith-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kaiser-chiefs">凯撒酋长队</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ricky-wilson">瑞奇·威尔逊 (Ricky Wilson)</a>回忆起过去他受到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-e-smith">马克·E·史密斯 (Mark E. Smith)</a>和绿洲乐队 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis)</a>的侮辱。</p><p>作为<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/kaiser-chiefs-boris-johnson-took-a-weird-dislike-to-our-band-and-i-dont-know-why-3576361">“摇滚乐会杀死脑细胞吗？！”</a>的一部分，接受<em>NME</em>采访<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/kaiser-chiefs-boris-johnson-took-a-weird-dislike-to-our-band-and-i-dont-know-why-3576361">在测验中</a>，威尔逊正确地猜出了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-fall">深秋</a>偶像史密斯曾经说过的“凯撒酋长队和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arctic-monkeys">北极猴子队</a>应该在北约克郡开设一家薯条连锁店”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kaiser-chiefs-how-2-dance-single-ricky-wilson-interview-new-album-nile-rodgers-rudimental-3342260">凯撒酋长谈论新专辑：“没有人阻止我们”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这一评论是 2006 年<a href="https://www.marksimpson.com/2006/07/29/the-north-rises-again-interview-with-mark-e-smith/#:~:text=%E2%80%9CI%20think%20that%20the%20Kaiser,relevant%2C%20like%20a%20classical%20composition." target="_blank" rel="noopener">采访</a>的一部分，史密斯在采访中补充道：“我认为东德人实际上是对的。每个团体过去都有许可证。在他们想出任何与文化相关的东西（比如古典作品）之前，我认为他们应该把它们带到这里。</p><p> “我应该开始一部音乐剧斯塔西。如果你不能在闲暇时间玩，那就滚回工厂吧。”</p><p>近二十年后，威尔逊在回应这一挖掘时告诉<em>《NME》</em> ：“我非常尊重和钦佩马克·E·史密斯，但如果他尊重我，我就会<em>少</em>尊重和钦佩他！” [<em>笑</em>]。”</p><p>他继续说道：“Mark E 干得好，<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/mark-e-smith-obituary-the-fall-2227837">安息吧</a>。但你知道吗，从来没有人说过他应该开一家名为 Marquee Smiths 的帐篷公司。”</p><p>在问答环节中，威尔逊被问及他在 2006 年 NME 颁奖典礼上击败哪四位艺人获得最佳着装奖。这促使主唱提醒<em>NME</em> ，他在获胜后“从未收到过单指敬礼小雕像”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="凯撒酋长队 - 感觉还不错（可视化工具）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jlaxGgWJV4M?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>威尔逊这次给出了错误的答案，然后被提醒，实际上是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brandon-flowers">布兰登·弗劳尔斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alex-kapranos">亚历克斯·卡普拉诺斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-doherty">皮特·多尔蒂</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔</a>。</p><p>他接着回忆道，他之前曾与绿洲乐队“见过面”，“但我们并没有嘲笑他们对我的旧事”。威尔逊补充道：“我不是那种会质问利亚姆·加拉格尔过去说过的关于我的事情的人，因为我确信他已经忘记了其中的大部分，而我不在乎。</p><p> “我想成为他的朋友吗？确实。我想我可以吗？可能不会。我认为他非常擅长搞笑。我不认为他曾经试图伤害我——希望他能长久地控制自己的欢闹。”</p><p>早在 2008 年，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kaiser-chiefs-111-1307346">威尔逊就曾表示 Oasis 已经“自己消失了”</a> 。他继续说道：“他们认为自己是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/led-zeppelin">齐柏林飞艇</a>。他们不是。音乐已经向前发展，我认为我们是大多数乐迷视为继任者的乐队。”</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/kaiser-chiefs-duck-review-2532330">凯撒酋长队 – “鸭子”评论</a></strong></li></ul><figure id="attachment_3521033" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3521033" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3521033" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KaiserChiefs-eighth-album-new-single-Feeling-Alright.jpg" alt="凯撒酋长队新闻图片" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KaiserChiefs-eighth-album-new-single-Feeling-Alright.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KaiserChiefs-eighth-album-new-single-Feeling-Alright-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KaiserChiefs-eighth-album-new-single-Feeling-Alright-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KaiserChiefs-eighth-album-new-single-Feeling-Alright-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KaiserChiefs-eighth-album-new-single-Feeling-Alright-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KaiserChiefs-eighth-album-new-single-Feeling-Alright-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3521033" class="wp-caption-text">凯撒酋长队。图片来源：卡尔·麦金太尔</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-439-1321258">那年晚些时候，诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 回击</a>道：“我吸毒 18 年了，但我从来没有犯过严重到说‘你知道吗？我认为凯撒酋长队非常出色。”</p><p> 2019 年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-calls-pissflap-kaiser-chiefs-keyboardist-peanut-stage-safety-row-2546885">利亚姆称​​凯撒队的键盘手花生是舞台安全排上的“小便”</a> 。 “正是像你这样的无赖给利兹联带来了坏名声，”他在推特上写道。</p><p>与此同时，Kaiser Chiefs 将于 3 月 1 日发行“Kaiser Chiefs&#39; Easy第八张专辑”（<a href="https://nfan.link/kaiser-chiefs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存</a>）。他们上个月分享了该项目的最新单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-kaiser-chiefs-disco-laced-new-single-burning-in-flames-3573626">“Burning In Flames”</a> 。</p><p>该乐队将于今年春天开始英国巡演—— <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3DKaiser%2520Chiefs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里找到剩余的门票</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kaiser-chiefs-ricky-wilson-responds-to-insults-received-from-mark-e-smith-and-oasis-3584979">凯撒酋长队的瑞奇·威尔逊 (Ricky Wilson) 对马克·E·史密斯 (Mark E. Smith) 和绿洲 (Oasis) 的侮辱做出回应，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
